  "ai_usage": "Use as a standalone pricing page. Wire a monthly/yearly switch (role='switch', aria-checked) that swaps each price from data-monthly/data-yearly and shows the annual saving; highlight one recommended tier. Provide a real <table> comparison with scope headers and a <details> FAQ. Recolor via --accent; edit prices/features. Keep the switch keyboard-operable and focus-visible.",
  "path": "effects/website-templates/pricing-page.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>Pricing Page</title>\n<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n{\n  \"id\": \"pricing-page\",\n  \"title\": \"Pricing Page\",\n  \"summary\": \"A dedicated pricing page: monthly/yearly toggle with live price swap, three tiers (one featured), a feature comparison table, and a pricing FAQ.\",\n  \"description\": \"The conversion-critical pricing page done properly — a billing toggle that updates all prices and shows the annual saving, three cards with a highlighted recommended plan, a detailed feature-comparison table, and an objection-handling FAQ.\",\n  \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n  \"categories\": [\"template\", \"saas\", \"pricing\"],\n  \"tags\": [\"pricing\", \"saas\", \"billing-toggle\", \"comparison\", \"faq\", \"full-page\"],\n  \"tech\": [\"html\", \"css\", \"js\"],\n  \"era\": \"2020s\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"intermediate\",\n  \"dependencies\": [],\n  \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers.\",\n  \"performance_notes\": \"A toggle that swaps prices via data attributes + reveals. No libraries.\",\n  \"accessibility_notes\": \"Billing toggle is a real switch (role/aria-checked, keyboard operable); the comparison is a real <table> with scope headers; FAQ uses <details>. Focus-visible throughout.\",\n  \"customization\": [\n    { \"name\": \"prices\", \"description\": \"data-monthly / data-yearly per tier\", \"default\": \"edit markup\" },\n    { \"name\": \"--accent\", \"description\": \"Brand + featured highlight\", \"default\": \"#7c5cff\" }\n  ],\n  \"variations\": [\"Add a usage-based slider\", \"Per-seat calculator\", \"Add a free tier column to the table\"],\n  \"related\": [\"saas-landing\", \"aurora-saas\", \"tilt-spotlight-card\"],\n  \"ai_usage\": \"Use as a standalone pricing page. Wire a monthly/yearly switch (role='switch', aria-checked) that swaps each price from data-monthly/data-yearly and shows the annual saving; highlight one recommended tier. Provide a real <table> comparison with scope headers and a <details> FAQ. Recolor via --accent; edit prices/features. Keep the switch keyboard-operable and focus-visible.\"\n}\n</script>\n<style>\n  :root{--bg:#0b0d12;--surface:#12151f;--line:#242a3b;--text:#e8ecf6;--muted:#8b93a7;--accent:#7c5cff;--accent2:#2dd4bf;--r:16px;}\n  *{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}\n  body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:\"Inter\",system-ui,sans-serif;line-height:1.6}\n  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n  .wrap{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.4rem}\n  nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:66px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}\n  .brand{font-weight:800}.links{display:flex;gap:1.4rem;color:var(--muted);font-size:.92rem}.links a:hover{color:var(--text)}\n  .head{text-align:center;padding:4rem 0 1rem}\n  .head h1{font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5vw,3.4rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:0 0 .5rem}\n  .head p{color:var(--muted);font-size:1.1rem}\n  .toggle{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:.8rem;justify-content:center;margin:1.6rem 0 .4rem}\n  .toggle .sw{width:54px;height:30px;border-radius:999px;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);position:relative;cursor:pointer}\n  .toggle .sw::after{content:\"\";position:absolute;top:3px;left:3px;width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);transition:transform .2s}\n  .toggle .sw[aria-checked=\"true\"]::after{transform:translateX(24px)}\n  .toggle .sw:focus-visible{outline:3px solid var(--accent2);outline-offset:3px}\n  .save{color:var(--accent2);font-size:.82rem;font-weight:700;background:rgba(45,212,191,.12);padding:.2rem .6rem;border-radius:999px}\n  .tiers{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.2rem;padding:1.5rem 0 1rem;align-items:start}\n  .tier{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--r);padding:1.8rem}\n  .tier.feat{border-color:transparent;background:linear-gradient(var(--surface),var(--surface)) padding-box,linear-gradient(135deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2)) border-box;border:2px solid transparent;position:relative}\n  .tier.feat .tag{position:absolute;top:-12px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:linear-gradient(120deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));color:#fff;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:800;padding:.25rem .8rem;border-radius:999px}\n  .tier h3{margin:0}.tier .desc{color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem;min-height:2.4em}\n  .price{font-size:2.6rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:.4rem 0 0}.price small{font-size:1rem;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500}\n  .tier ul{list-style:none;padding:0;margin:1.2rem 0;color:var(--muted)}\n  .tier li{padding:.3rem 0}.tier li::before{content:\"✓ \";color:var(--accent2)}\n  .btn{display:block;text-align:center;border-radius:12px;padding:.85rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--text)}\n  .btn.primary{background:linear-gradient(120deg,var(--accent),var(--accent2));color:#fff;border:none}\n  .btn:focus-visible{outline:3px solid var(--accent2);outline-offset:2px}\n  section{padding:3rem 0}\n  h2{text-align:center;font-size:clamp(1.7rem,3.4vw,2.3rem);font-weight:800;margin:0 0 1.6rem}\n  table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:.95rem}\n  th,td{padding:.85rem 1rem;text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}\n  th[scope=\"col\"]{font-size:1rem}td:first-child,th:first-child{text-align:left;color:var(--muted)}\n  tbody tr:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02)}\n  .y{color:var(--accent2)}.n{color:#4a5266}\n  .faq{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto}\n  details{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding:1rem 0}summary{cursor:pointer;font-weight:700;list-style:none;display:flex;justify-content:space-between}\n  summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}details[open] summary{color:var(--accent2)}\n  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);text-align:center;padding:2.2rem 0;font-size:.9rem}\n  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:opacity .6s,transform .6s ease}.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}\n  @media(max-width:820px){.tiers{grid-template-columns:1fr}.links{display:none}table{font-size:.82rem}th,td{padding:.6rem .4rem}}\n  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}html{scroll-behavior:auto}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <nav><div class=\"brand\">◆ Nimbus</div><div class=\"links\"><a href=\"#\">Product</a><a href=\"#\">Customers</a><a href=\"#\">Docs</a><a href=\"#\">Sign in</a></div></nav>\n\n    <header class=\"head\">\n      <h1>Simple pricing that scales with you</h1>\n      <p>Start free. Upgrade when you're ready. Cancel anytime.</p>\n      <div class=\"toggle\">\n        <span>Monthly</span>\n        <span class=\"sw\" id=\"sw\" role=\"switch\" aria-checked=\"false\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"Toggle yearly billing\"></span>\n        <span>Yearly <span class=\"save\">Save 20%</span></span>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"tiers\">\n      <div class=\"tier reveal\">\n        <h3>Starter</h3><p class=\"desc\">For individuals getting started.</p>\n        <div class=\"price\" data-monthly=\"$0\" data-yearly=\"$0\">$0<small>/mo</small></div>\n        <ul><li>1 project</li><li>Community support</li><li>1 GB storage</li></ul>\n        <a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Start free</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tier feat reveal\">\n        <span class=\"tag\">Most popular</span>\n        <h3>Pro</h3><p class=\"desc\">For growing teams that ship.</p>\n        <div class=\"price\" data-monthly=\"$29\" data-yearly=\"$23\">$29<small>/mo</small></div>\n        <ul><li>Unlimited projects</li><li>Priority support</li><li>100 GB storage</li><li>Advanced analytics</li></ul>\n        <a class=\"btn primary\" href=\"#\">Choose Pro</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tier reveal\">\n        <h3>Enterprise</h3><p class=\"desc\">For organizations at scale.</p>\n        <div class=\"price\" data-monthly=\"$99\" data-yearly=\"$79\">$99<small>/mo</small></div>\n        <ul><li>Everything in Pro</li><li>SSO &amp; SAML</li><li>Dedicated SLA</li><li>Onboarding</li></ul>\n        <a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Contact sales</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <section>\n      <h2 class=\"reveal\">Compare plans</h2>\n      <table>\n        <thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"></th><th scope=\"col\">Starter</th><th scope=\"col\">Pro</th><th scope=\"col\">Enterprise</th></tr></thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr><td>Projects</td><td>1</td><td>Unlimited</td><td>Unlimited</td></tr>\n          <tr><td>Storage</td><td>1 GB</td><td>100 GB</td><td>1 TB</td></tr>\n          <tr><td>Analytics</td><td class=\"n\">—</td><td class=\"y\">✓</td><td class=\"y\">✓</td></tr>\n          <tr><td>SSO &amp; SAML</td><td class=\"n\">—</td><td class=\"n\">—</td><td class=\"y\">✓</td></tr>\n          <tr><td>Dedicated SLA</td><td class=\"n\">—</td><td class=\"n\">—</td><td class=\"y\">✓</td></tr>\n          <tr><td>Support</td><td>Community</td><td>Priority</td><td>Dedicated</td></tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </section>\n\n    <section>\n      <h2 class=\"reveal\">Pricing FAQ</h2>\n      <div class=\"faq reveal\">\n        <details><summary>Can I change plans later?<span>+</span></summary><p class=\"muted\" style=\"color:var(--muted)\">Yes — upgrade or downgrade anytime; we prorate the difference automatically.</p></details>\n        <details><summary>Is there a free trial?<span>+</span></summary><p style=\"color:var(--muted)\">Pro includes a 14-day free trial, no card required.</p></details>\n        <details><summary>What payment methods do you accept?<span>+</span></summary><p style=\"color:var(--muted)\">All major cards, and invoicing on Enterprise.</p></details>\n        <details><summary>Do you offer discounts?<span>+</span></summary><p style=\"color:var(--muted)\">Yearly billing saves 20%, plus discounts for students and nonprofits.</p></details>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>© <span id=\"yr\"></span> Nimbus, Inc. · Questions? sales@nimbus.dev</footer>\n  </div>\n  <script>\n    document.getElementById('yr').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();\n    var sw=document.getElementById('sw');\n    function setBilling(yearly){\n      sw.setAttribute('aria-checked',yearly);\n      document.querySelectorAll('.price').forEach(function(p){\n        var v=yearly?p.dataset.yearly:p.dataset.monthly;\n        p.innerHTML=v+'<small>/mo</small>';\n      });\n    }\n    sw.addEventListener('click',function(){setBilling(sw.getAttribute('aria-checked')!=='true');});\n    sw.addEventListener('keydown',function(e){if(e.key===' '||e.key==='Enter'){e.preventDefault();setBilling(sw.getAttribute('aria-checked')!=='true');}});\n    var io=new IntersectionObserver(function(es){es.forEach(function(e){if(e.isIntersecting){e.target.classList.add('in');io.unobserve(e.target)}})},{threshold:.12});\n    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(function(el){io.observe(el)});\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
